<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Physicians Claim Partners</title>

  <!-- CONTROL+F: STYLE START -->
  <style>
    body{
      margin:0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background:#f9fbfd;
      color:#222;
    }

    .section{
      padding:80px 6%;
    }

    h2{
      font-size:36px;
      margin-bottom:10px;
    }

    p{
      font-size:16px;
      line-height:1.6;
    }

    /* IMAGE BLOCKS */
    .grid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit,minmax(300px,1fr));
      gap:40px;
      margin-top:50px;
    }

    .card{
      background:#fff;
      border-radius:20px;
      padding:30px;
      box-shadow:0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
      transition:.4s;
    }

    .card:hover{
      transform:translateY(-8px) rotateY(6deg);
    }

    .img-box{
      height:260px;
      border-radius:18px;
      background-size:cover;
      background-position:center;
      margin-bottom:20px;
      animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes float{
      0%{transform:translateY(0)}
      50%{transform:translateY(-12px)}
      100%{transform:translateY(0)}
    }
  </style>
  <!-- CONTROL+F: STYLE END -->
</head>
</body><!-- CONTROL+F: CODING SECTION -->
<section class="section" id="coding">

  <h2>ICD-10 / ICD-11 / CPT / CDT Coding Expertise</h2>
  <p>
    We support multi-specialty practices with accurate diagnosis-procedure pairing
    using current ICD-10, ICD-11, CPT and CDT standards.
  </p>

  <div class="grid">

    <div class="card">
      <div class="img-box" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580281657521-6b38c2d2c6a8?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200');"></div>
      <h3>ICD-10 & ICD-11</h3>
      <p>
        Coding aligned with CMS, WHO and payer-specific rules.
        Covers internal medicine, psychiatry, surgery and multi-specialty practices.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="img-box" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1554224155-6726b3ff858f?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200');"></div>
      <h3>Real CPT Pairing</h3>
      <p>
        Accurate E/M leveling, surgical coding and modifier usage based on documentation.
        Prevents under-coding and denials.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="img-box" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1606813902914-5f39a1f92e86?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200');"></div>
      <h3>CDT (Dental Coding)</h3>
      <p>
        Correct CDT usage, PPO fee schedules and narrative-based submissions
        to maximize dental reimbursements.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
<!-- CONTROL+F: CODING SECTION END -->
</body>
</html>
